const twoDigitYears = require('./twoDigitYears.js');
const timezoneNames = require('./timezoneNames.js');

const baseLookups = {
	zone: timezoneNames,
	year: twoDigitYears,
	meridiem: { am: 0, pm: 12, 'a.m.': 0, 'p.m.': 12 },
	month: {
		january: 1,
		jan: 1,
		february: 2,
		feb: 2,
		march: 3,
		mar: 3,
		april: 4,
		apr: 4,
		may: 5,
		june: 6,
		jun: 6,
		july: 7,
		jul: 7,
		august: 8,
		aug: 8,
		september: 9,
		sep: 9,
		october: 10,
		oct: 10,
		november: 11,
		nov: 11,
		december: 12,
		dec: 12,
	},
	dayname: {
		sunday: 0,
		sun: 0,
		monday: 1,
		mon: 1,
		tuesday: 2,
		tue: 2,
		wednesday: 3,
		wed: 3,
		thursday: 4,
		thu: 4,
		friday: 5,
		fri: 5,
		saturday: 6,
		sat: 6,
	},
	digit: {},
};

module.exports = baseLookups;
